outputs.output_descr: The project is to support implementing activities of the Information Technology Institute aimed at providing the Egyptian Public and Private labor market with a pool of highly qualified IT professionals and entrepreneurs via  a) supporting Innovation and entrepreneurship across ITI and private sector promoted. b) enhancing employability skills of the youth and creation of new job opportunities and c) enhancing of ITI international cooperation relations

project_descr: Supporting  the Activities of the Information Technology Institute (ITI) -Phase II
